  <name>GTKCrypto</name>
  <summary>GTK+ application for encrypting files and computing hashes</summary>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>aes</keyword>
    <keyword>twofish</keyword>
    <keyword>serpent</keyword>
    <keyword>md5</keyword>
    <keyword>sha2</keyword>
    <keyword>sha3</keyword>
    <keyword>gost</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <description>
    <p>
GTKCrypto allows you to encrypt and sign files or text. Moreover, given a file, different types of hash can be computed and files can also be compared to check whether or not their content is the same.
Supported cipher algorithms: AES, Twofish, Serpent and Camellia, all using 256 bits key and operating in either CBC or CTR mode.
Supported hash algorithms: MD5, SHA-1, SHA-2, SHA-3, GOST, Whirlpool.
    </p>
  </description>

